attributionInfo.brokerName: Keller Williams Realty Boston-Metro | Back Bay

description: This sun-filled home features soaring ceilings, gleaming hardwood floors, and oversized windows that flood the space with natural light. Versatile sliding pocket doors create flexible options for privacy, entertaining, or open living. The kitchen features modern cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, a stylish backsplash, and granite countertops. The king-sized primary bedroom offers an en-suite bath, while the second bedroom comfortably fits a queen bed and includes generous closet space. Enjoy the convenience of in-unit laundry, central A/C, deeded storage, and one heated garage parking space. A prime location just two blocks from the Broadway T Station, with easy access to acclaimed restaurants, Seaport, Downtown, South End, highways, and the airport.
